
Image formats:
 - xpm
 - ico (Windows Icon)
 - (e)ps
 - pcx
 - targa
 - all the others

General:
 - make Loaders (-> Codecs) read write from c++ streams - so users can
   extend it beyond current limits (that is from memory and network streams)
 - Exif, XMP and ordinary, classic comment support 

Loders:
 - allow for jpeg scaling / orthogonal rotation without recompression

Algorithms:
 - scaling!
 - rotation, descew
 - descreen
 - sharp, unsharp
 - crop
 - all the others

Colorspaces:
 - CMYK
 - YUV
 - sRGB vs. Adobe RGB
 - ...

Frontends:
 - more complete edentify
 - edisplay thumbnailing, slideshow, information blending

